\subsection*{14.4 Results: $\beta$ Dependence at Fixed Volume ($16 \times 8^3$)}

We study $\beta$ dependence on a $16 \times 8^3$ lattice.

\begin{table}[H]
	\centering
	\caption{Scale setting results for different $\beta$ values at $16 \times 8^3$}
	\begin{tabular}{|c|c|c|c|c|c|c|}
		\hline
		$\beta$ & $r_0/a$ & $a$ (fm) & $t_0/a^2$ & $\sqrt{t_0}/a$ & $a$ (flow) (fm) & Difference \\
		\hline
